{"tid":1242283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元：612疑有警方混入示威者挖磚，企圖合理化之後中信催淚彈事件！","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T04:35:34.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0894c950260ae3012e29b4f74390153106a2c39d","tid":1242283,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zpLaUa9iWj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzpLaUa9iWj4&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dYc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=2fb623c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zpLaUa9iWj4</a><br />\n<br />\n首先有不明來歷估計是警方派人混入示威群眾人士挖磚，企圖引誘示威者掟磚，方便警方大條道理鎭壓，其後蕭生都見到有數人掟磚。<br />\n<br />\n估計有人一早已與警方通水如何將武力鎮壓升級，否則難以解釋為何警方増援同鎮壓得咁快，再派人混入示威者引誘示威者使用爆力，令警方鎮壓有理。今次警察係為左報仇，目的係要打到你驚而唔係驅散你地，中信催淚彈事件就係例子，亦證明以上陰謀確切無疑！"},{"pid":"f8e766a622ffeb2f17400dfbad310a1b128d6e30","tid":1242283,"uid":57797,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"即係冇警方混入示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd247cb6fb7b898c792168bad01ca86943e3d0e8","tid":1242283,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"蕭生給大家的警示：小心衝擊的人！"},{"pid":"c399fffeed8f74545af63d5373bc76284e43b20d","tid":1242283,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"燒山知自己燈就收聲喇 屌你老母"},{"pid":"5acbb91638ab11fc7e2f4961d41a8b2f944f4c70","tid":1242283,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee19d62ae342f475efbf469b789d2eef9fe1594c","tid":1242283,"uid":50762,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"即係無鬼啊<br />\n咪撚再郁啲就話鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj